<hr />
<p>Hello everyone, Camileytor2008 here. This is my SCP Art Diary, a personal project I began for my own amusement and as an attempt to try different things with my art style.</p>
<p>In a handmade sketchbook I've decided to draw daily as many SCPs as I can, ranging from the most classic and recognizable of them to some I feel deserve more love. I hope you enjoy them.</p>
<p>Huge thanks to <span class="error-inline"><em>UncannyClown276</em> does not match any existing user name</span> for encouraging me and helping me to get this little Art page running.</p>
<hr />
